  "translations": {
    "en": "Then it transformed into the form in which it had been with Adam in Paradise, and said to Adam: 'Where is the covenant and the primordial pledge?' Adam leapt towards it, remembered the primordial pledge, wept, humbled himself before it, kissed it, and renewed the affirmation of the covenant and the primordial pledge. Then Allah the Mighty and Majestic transformed it into the gemstone of the Black Stone — a white, pure, radiating pearl.",
